Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 方便说话吗？ - 说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Got a minute? - A minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有觉得史波克有点不对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's Spock. You noticed anything strange about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没感觉，为什么这么说？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, nothing in particular. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然彻底检查之前我不能确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it's nothing I can pinpoint without an examination,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他现在越来越躁动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but he's become increasingly restive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他不是瓦肯，那可以说是“紧张”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If he were not a Vulcan, I'd almost say "nervous."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,另外他现在拒绝进食\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For another thing, he's avoiding food.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我确认他已经三天没吃东西了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've checked and he hasn't eaten at all in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来史波克先生进入冥想阶段了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, that just sounds like Mr. Spock in one of his contemplative phases.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,查佩尔小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miss Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 麦考伊医生 - 舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Dr. McCoy. - Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯族的普罗米克汤，肯定是你做的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vulcan plomeek soup. And I'll bet you made it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你从来不死心，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You never give up hoping, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是碰巧发现史波克先生没有吃东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock hasn't been eating, Doctor. And I just happened to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系，你去吧，查佩尔小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's all right. Carry on, Miss Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 老骨头，我要去忙了 - 吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bones, I'm a busy man. - Jim,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议史波克进行常规体检的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when I suggested to Spock it was time for his routine checkup
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你理智的大副对我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}your logical, unemotional first officer turned to me and said:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻停止对我的窥探，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"You will cease to pry into my personal matters, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我扭断你的脖子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or I shall certainly break your neck."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克这么说？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么破东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,又是监视，窥探，如果有需要，我自己会说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Poking. Prying. If I want anything from you, I'll ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我想请假回自己的星球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I should like to request a leave of absence. On my home planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从现行轨道绕去瓦肯，只会损失2.8光天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On our present course, you can divert to Vulcan with a loss of but 2.8 light-days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到底出了什么鬼事？ - 我已经提出请求了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What the devil is this all about? - I've made my request, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要你一个答案，允许还是不允许\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I require from you is that you answer it, yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00DA4E&}-=THE LAST FANTASY=-\N荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：gosiwi\N校对：喜马拉雅{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,第二季第一集\N狂躁时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好，史波克，说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, Spock. Let's have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,取悦一个陌生男性，对女人来说有点不检点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is undignified for a woman to play servant to a man who is not hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是聊聊你的请假吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm more interested in your request for shore leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 根据这些年… - 你已经知道我的请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- In the years that I've known... - You have my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你批准吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you grant it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,根据这些年我对你的了解，你从未要求请假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In all the years I've known you, you've never asked for leave of any sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你甚至拒绝了，为什么现在要请假？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In fact, you've refused them. Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，显然我已经积累了足够的假期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, surely I have enough leave time accumulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，但这不是主要问题，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Agreed. But that isn't the question, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果出现一些情况，比如家人重病…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's a problem of some sort, illness in the family...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有那回事，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing of that nature, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就去牛郎星6号行星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then since we're headed for Altair VI,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而且星球上有先进的设备…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and since the shore facilities there are excellent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我必须…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望能请假去瓦肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish to take my leave on Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我问你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请你接受这个回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm asking you to accept that answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舵手 - 是，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Helm. - Yes, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,转向去瓦肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alter course to Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 加速到曲速四 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Increase speed to warp 4. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看来大部分人都没意识到瓦肯人也有脆弱的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I suppose most of us overlook the fact that even Vulcans aren't indestructible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是坚不可摧的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3372.7\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's Log, Stardate 3372.7.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如计划行驶，经瓦肯前往牛郎星6号行星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On course, on schedule, bound for Altair VI via Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大副史波克似乎压力巨大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First Officer Spock seems to be under stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他要求请假去瓦肯并已获批\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He has requested and been granted shore leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生已在监护他的身体状况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship's Surgeon McCoy has him under medical surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，舰队频道上有情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, something's coming in on the Starfleet channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急状况，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Priority and urgent, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,传过来，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put it on audio over here, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,消息转换完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Message complete, sir. Switching over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,星际舰队第9分队致联邦星舰进取号舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To Captain, U.S.S. Enterprise. From Starfleet, Sector 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,牛郎星6号就职典礼提前7个太阳日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Inauguration ceremonies Altair VI have been advanced seven solar days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现命令你按照要求改变飞行计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're ordered to alter your flight plan as filed to accommodate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队司令部寇马克上将令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By order of Komack, Admiral, Starfleet Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,乌乎拉上尉，接受这个指令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Uhura, acknowledge that message.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,契诃夫先生，计算调整所需轨道和航速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov, compute course and speed necessary for compliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须以曲速六直趋前往\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll have to head directly there at warp 6, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间停留在瓦肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Insufficient time to stop off at Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,直趋前往牛郎星6号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Head directly for Altair VI.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,水手的运气，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sailor's luck, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,简直就像墨菲定理：\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or, as one of Finagle's Laws puts it:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,每艘船停留的港湾总是别人的家乡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Any home port the ship makes will be somebody else's, not mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,牛郎星6号的新总统想提前一周就职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The new President of Altair VI wants to get himself launched a week early,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们必须提前到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so we have to be there a week early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要担心，我会给你假期的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't worry, I'll see that you get your leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦就职典礼结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as soon as we're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全理解，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I quite understand, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰桥，导航部 - 导航部，契诃夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bridge, Navigation. - Navigation, Chekov here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,契诃夫，如果我们以最大速度绕道至瓦肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov, how late will we arrive for the ceremonies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把史波克丢上岸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if we increase speed to maximum and divert to Vulcan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,最晚会什么时候达到典礼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just long enough to drop off Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不理解，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not understand, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会耽搁多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How far behind schedule will diverting to Vulcan put us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在前往瓦肯，舰长，是史波克先生命令的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're on course for Vulcan, Captain, as Mr. Spock ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，契诃夫先生，寇克完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, Mr. Chekov. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come with me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,5号舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Deck 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么变更航道去瓦肯，史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You changed course for Vulcan, Mr. Spock. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,变更航道？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Changed the course?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你否认吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不，一点不否认，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. By no means, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我很可能这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is quite possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么？ - 舰长，我承认你所说的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Then why did you do it? - Captain, I accept, on your word...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...that I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我也不知道为什么，我也不记得我这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I do not know why, nor do I remember doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，把我锁起来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, lock me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想见任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not wish to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯族人不能再做更多解释了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot. No Vulcan could explain further.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我在帮你，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm trying to help you, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别问了，我不会回答的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ask me no further questions. I will not answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我命令你去医务室报道 - 医务室？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I order you to report to the Sickbay. - Sickbay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,完成体检，麦考伊在等着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Complete examination. McCoy's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,请进，史波克，我已经准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come in, Spock. I'm all ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的命令是向医务室报道，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My orders were to report to Sickbay, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have done so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要回自己的船舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now I'll go to my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到的命令是给你一个全面的体检\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My orders were to give you a thorough physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你没意识到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In case you hadn't noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们下命令的是同一个军官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to answer to the same commanding officer that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,理智一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yield to the logic of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,给我体检吧，好让我们都交差\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Examine me, for all the good it will do either of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想，契诃夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you figure it, Chekov?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始，我们去瓦肯，然后我们去牛郎星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First we're going to Vulcan. Then we're going to Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,之后又要去瓦肯，这下又得去牛郎星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then we're headed to Vulcan again. Now we're headed back to Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会晕舱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I'm going to get space-sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，你必须送史波克去瓦肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, you've got to get Spock to Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，我会的，一旦任务结束之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, I will, I will. As soon as this mission is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，立刻，如果你不在一星期内把他送去瓦肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, now. Right away. If you don't get him to Vulcan within a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再在外面待八天，他就会死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}eight days at the outside, he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他会死的，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'll die, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,…为什么一定会在八天内死？解释清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...must he die? Why within eight days? Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直这么说，你不是个医生吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You keep saying that. Are you a doctor or aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他的机体失衡越来越严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a growing imbalance of body functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像我们体内的肾上腺素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As if in our bodies, huge amounts of adrenaline
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不断涌入血管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}were constantly being pumped into our bloodstreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我的电脑不能追踪出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, I can't trace it down in my bio-comps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克不愿意告诉我是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock won't tell me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果这种激素不停止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if it isn't stopped somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,体能和精神上的压力会把他压垮致死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the physical and emotional pressures will simply kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定他知道是什么吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You say you're convinced he knows what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但他像毕宿五的贝类一样守口如瓶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he's as tightlipped about it as an Aldebaran shellmouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,问他没用的，吉姆，他不会说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No use to ask him, Jim. He won't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不用起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊已经给我你的体检报告了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy has given me his medical evaluation of your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他说如果不采取行动的话你就会死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He says you're going to die unless something is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是只有你的母星能解救你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it something only your planet can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是全舰队最好的大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've been called the best first officer in the Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我来说非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's an enormous asset to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我要失去一个大副，我要知道是为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I have to lose that first officer, I want to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个没有外邦人知道的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a thing no outworlder may know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,除了那些少数被卷入其中的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...except those very few who've been involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人知道，但是我们之间也不会提及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A Vulcan understands, but even we do not speak of it among ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个非常私人的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is a deeply personal thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你能明白吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you see that, Captain, and understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白，解释给我听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I do not understand. Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Consider that an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有的事是超乎命令的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are some things which transcend even the discipline of the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would it help if I told you that I'll treat this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保守这个秘密的，你能告诉我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as totally confidential?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟生理有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has to do with biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？ - 生理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - Biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么生理？ - 瓦肯生理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What kind of biology? - Vulcan biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是，瓦肯人的生理？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean, the biology of Vulcans?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,繁衍生理？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Biology as in reproduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好害羞的，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...there's no need to be embarrassed about it, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,鸟类和蜂类也有这种情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It happens to the birds and bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,鸟和蜂不是瓦肯人，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The birds and the bees are not Vulcans, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they were,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果任何生物像我们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if any creature as proudly logical as us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有逻辑思维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}were to have their logic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种时刻都会失去理智…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ripped from them as this time does to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人怎么选择配偶？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do Vulcans choose their mates?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你有想过吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Haven't you wondered?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I guess the rest of us assume that it's done...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,…很理智的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...quite logically.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们沿袭古老的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We shield it with ritual...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,传统和习俗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and customs shrouded in antiquity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你们无法想象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You humans have no conception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它剥夺我们的理智\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It strips our minds from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,剥下我们文明的外衣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It brings a madness which
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,使我们变得疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}rips away our veneer of civilisation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫逄会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is the Pon farr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说交配时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The time of mating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是有自然的先例的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are precedents in nature, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,轩辕五的鸟鳗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The giant eel-birds of Regulus V,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,每11年就会回到他们出生的洞穴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}once each 11 years they must return to the caverns where they hatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上的鲑鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On your Earth, salmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必须回到那条小溪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They must return to that one stream
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们出生的地方繁殖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where they were born to spawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,或者死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or die in trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不是鱼，史波克先生，你是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you're not a fish, Mr. Spock. You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我也不是人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, nor am I a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是瓦肯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我能躲过这劫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had hoped I would be spared this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,…但古老的欲望太强烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...but the ancient drives are too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,最后会吞没我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eventually they catch up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们无法控制这股力量…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we are driven by forces we cannot control...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,…然后回家…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...to return home...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,…娶妻…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and take a wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,…或死去…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会当作什么都没听到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I haven't heard a word you've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而且…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想办法带你回瓦肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll get you to Vulcan. Somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，帮我联系舰队司令部第九分队寇马克上将\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant, get me Admiral Komack at Starfleet Command, Sector 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接到麦考伊办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pipe it down to McCoy's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队司令部，是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Starfleet Command. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁先生，你该不会认为…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Sulu, you don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许该准备一条回瓦肯的路，以防万一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe you ought to plot a course back to Vulcan, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,联系史波克先生，我是乌乎拉上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Communication to Mr. Spock. Lieutenant Uhura here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长让我通知你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain asked me to inform you he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让我一个人静一静！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你的要求并非寻常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, you're making a most unusual request.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，但是也非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm aware of that, sir. But it's of the utmost importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,您一定要批准我绕道去瓦肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must give me permission to divert to Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但你拒绝解释为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you refuse to explain why it is so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能解释，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但请相信我，我不会恳请…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But believe me, I wouldn't make such a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,牛郎6号可不是个平常事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Altair VI is no ordinary matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方好不容易在星际纷争后得以恢复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That area is just putting itself together after a long interplanetary conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就职典礼会安抚整个牛郎星星系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This inauguration will stabilise the entire Altair system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的出现是友谊的象征\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our appearance there is a demonstration of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是对克林贡帝国有力的震慑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and strength which will cause ripples clear to the Klingon Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,先生…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们绝对不会延迟超过一天，我不相信…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the delay would be at most a day. I can hardly believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克，按照命令去牛郎6号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk, you will proceed to Altair VI as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么说，执行你的命令，完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The subject is closed. You have your orders. Starfleet out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看来只能这么办了 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well, that's that. - No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白牛郎星的局势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know the Altair situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,算上我们会有三艘星舰，气派而且带着外交使命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We would be one of three starships. Very impressive, very diplomatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没那么重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's simply not that vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能违背命令去瓦肯，你会被惩罚的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't go off to Vulcan against Starfleet orders. You'll be busted...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能眼睁睁看着史波克死啊，老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't let Spock die, can I, Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们去牛郎星他必死无疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he will if we go to Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他救了我那么多次性命，难道不值我牺牲事业救他？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I owe him my life a dozen times over. Isn't that worth a career?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰桥，导航部 - 舰桥，导航部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bridge. Navigation. - Bridge. Navigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,契诃夫先生…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,…设计线路去瓦肯，告诉轮机部要曲速八或更快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...lay in a course for Vulcan. Tell Engineering I want warp 8 or better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,以最快速度前行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Push her for all she'll take.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,线路已预备好，开始执行中，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Course already plotted. Laying it in, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，契诃夫先生，寇克退出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see. Very well. Carry on, Mr. Chekov. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,查佩尔小姐？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miss Chapel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是，史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了一个…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,…噩梦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...a most startling dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你在跟我说话…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were trying to tell me something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,…但我听不见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...but I couldn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,跟自己的本性抗争…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would be illogical for us to protest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,…是无谓的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...against our natures...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,…你觉得呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你流泪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your face is wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我过来告诉你我们要去瓦肯星了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I came to tell you that we are bound for Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,过不了几天我们就到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be there in just a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 查佩尔小姐 - 我叫克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Miss Chapel. - My name is Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I know, Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以为我做点普罗米克汤吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you make me some of that plomeek soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，我非常愿意，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I'd be very glad to do that, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,显然你已经猜到我的问题了，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's obvious that you've surmised my problem, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我钦佩你的洞察力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and my compliments on your insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，瓦肯正发生一件大事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, there is a thing that happens to Vulcans at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,非常疯狂，你应该会反感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}almost an insanity, which you would no doubt find distasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经对我的疯狂表现出极大的忍耐了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've been most patient with my kinds of madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以和我一起去瓦肯站在我边上吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then would you beam down to the planet surface and stand with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个简短的仪式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is a brief ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能被允许吗？ - 这是我的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is it permitted? - It is my right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,按照传统，男方可以由最好的朋友陪伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By tradition, the male is accompanied by his closest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也请求麦考伊陪我一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I also request McCoy accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的荣幸，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I shall be honoured, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们正处于瓦肯的欢迎频段，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...we're standing by on Vulcan hailing frequencies, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,打开频道，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Open channel, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯中心，这里是联邦星舰进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vulcan Space Central, this is the U.S.S. Enterprise
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,请求进入轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}requesting permission to assume standard orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦星舰进取号，批准进入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}U.S.S. Enterprise from Vulcan Space Central, permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,全体瓦肯欢迎你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And from all of Vulcan, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克在吗？ - 我是史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is Commander Spock with you? - This is Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请站好以激活中央显示屏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by to activate your central viewer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，发生什么事了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is I.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,提普灵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}T'Pring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,离别却从未离去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Parted from me and never parted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,从未接触\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never and always touching...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.60,0:23:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但始终相联\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.77,0:23:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在相约之地见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We meet at the appointed place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，离别却从未离去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock. Parted from me and never parted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,从未接触但始终相联\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never and always touching and touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I await you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.38,0:23:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她很漂亮，史波克先生，她是谁？ - 她是提普灵…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- She's lovely, Mr. Spock. Who is she? - She is T'Pring...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.97,0:23:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,…我的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.09,0:24:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的乡土\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the land of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.68,0:24:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的家族在此生存了2000个地球年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has been held by us for more than 2000 Earth years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.43,0:24:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们库努卡里菲的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is our place of Koon-ut-kal-if-fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.23,0:24:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他说库努什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He called it Koon-ut what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.11,0:24:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他的意思是“婚姻或决斗”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He described it to me as meaning "marriage or challenge."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.16,0:25:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,过去，瓦肯人要为爱人决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the distant past, Vulcans killed to win their mates.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.37,0:25:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们仍为此疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they still go mad at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.46,0:25:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,代价就是余生不再有感情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps the price they pay for having no emotions the rest of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.13,0:25:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好地方，如果来点凉风就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lovely. I wish the breeze were cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.84,0:25:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，我总算体会到“热得像瓦肯”的含义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. "Hot as Vulcan." Now I understand what that phrase means.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.56,0:25:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的大气比地球稀薄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The atmosphere is thinner than Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.52,0:25:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道提普灵什么时候到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wonder when his T'Pring arrives?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.32,0:25:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,婚礼盛典要开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The marriage party approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.49,0:25:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.16,0:25:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,婚礼盛典？我以为提普灵已经是你的妻子了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Marriage party? You said T'Pring was your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.58,0:25:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们父母定的亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By our parents' arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.96,0:25:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们只有7岁的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.96,0:25:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,举行过一个仪式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...while we were but 7 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.63,0:25:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是婚礼，倒不如说是定亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Less than a marriage, but more than a betrothal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.76,0:25:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,碰一下对方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One touches the other
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.52,0:26:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,接触到对方的思想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in order to feel each other's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.85,0:26:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,通过这样，我们的思想就被锁在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In this way, our minds were locked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.61,0:26:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,时候到来…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So that at the proper time...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.86,0:26:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们就会被吸引到…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...we would both be drawn to...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.37,0:26:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,…库努卡里菲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}... Koon-ut-kal-if-fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.17,0:26:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，知道那是谁吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, do you know who that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.93,0:27:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,提咆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}T'Pau.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.35,0:27:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是唯一一个拒绝联邦议会席位的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only person to ever turn down a seat in the Federation Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.35,0:27:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,提咆？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}T'Pau?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.31,0:27:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,主持史波克的婚礼？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Officiating at Spock's wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.77,0:27:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他从没提过他家族这么显赫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He never mentioned that his family was this important.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.16,0:28:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.87,0:28:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们的仪式是给外人看的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...are our ceremonies for outworlders?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.34,0:28:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不是外人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They are not outworlders.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.26,0:28:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.72,0:28:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我有权这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am permitted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.11,0:28:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.61,0:28:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.45,0:28:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫？ - 伦纳德·麦考伊，夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And thee are called? - Leonard McCoy, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.54,0:28:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你把这些外人称作朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thee names these outworlders "friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.88,0:28:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能负责他们的行为？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How does thee pledge their behaviour?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.80,0:28:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我以性命担保，提咆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With my life, T'Pau.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.30,0:29:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们将要看到的是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What thee are about to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.89,0:29:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,…从远古流传下来的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...comes down from the time of the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.23,0:29:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,…亘古不变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...without change.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.81,0:29:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是瓦肯的心，瓦肯的灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the Vulcan heart. This is the Vulcan soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.15,0:29:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的生活方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.30,0:30:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么？发生什么了？ - 她选择了决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What is it? What happened? - She chooses the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.81,0:30:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,和他？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.81,0:30:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他是处理懦夫的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He acts only if cowardice is seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.11,0:30:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她会选择她的代表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She will choose her champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.33,0:30:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.45,0:30:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要和他说话，寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do not attempt to speak with him, Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.49,0:30:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他身陷普拉克托，血热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He is deep in the plak tow, the blood fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.92,0:30:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在他通过历练之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He will not speak with thee again
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.46,0:30:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不会和你说话的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until he has passed through what is to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.59,0:30:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想离开…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If thee wishes to depart...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.68,0:30:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,…现在就可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...thee may leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.98,0:31:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.02,0:31:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克果然没看错人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock chose his friends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.40,0:31:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人，我不理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ma'am, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.86,0:31:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是她拒绝了他？她不想要他？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you trying to say that she rejected him. That she doesn't want him?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.57,0:31:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他必须为她决斗，这是她的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He will have to fight for her. It is her right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.46,0:31:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,提普灵，你已经选择了卡里菲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}T'Pring, thee has chosen the kal-if-fee...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,…即决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.21,0:31:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好成为胜者的战利品吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thee are prepared to become the property of the victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.43,0:31:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.52,0:31:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.82,0:31:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意根据律法和传统接受挑战吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does thee accept challenge, according to our laws and customs?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.50,0:31:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得史波克能赢得了他吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think Spock can take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.55,0:32:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我表示怀疑，他现在情况不佳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I doubt it. Not in his present condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.84,0:32:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,提普灵，你选择你的代表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}T'Pring, thee will choose thy champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.63,0:32:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,生命之初\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As it was in the dawn of our days,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.61,0:32:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就如今晨的黎明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as it is today
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.61,0:32:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,和所有的明天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as it will be for all tomorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.53,0:32:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I make my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.29,0:32:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.88,0:32:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.92,0:32:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am to be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.63,0:32:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她答应过的 - 安静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It was agreed. - Be silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.97,0:32:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.84,0:32:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我提出了古老的要求，我要求这个权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have made the ancient claim. I claim the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.14,0:32:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The woman is...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.36,0:32:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,请宽恕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I ask forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.82,0:33:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.45,0:33:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,…提普灵的要求是合理的，但我们的律法和传统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...T'Pring is within her rights, but our laws and customs...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.49,0:33:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,…并不制约你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...are not binding on thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.66,0:33:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以自己决定…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thee are free to decline...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.25,0:33:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会强加于你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...with no harm on thyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.98,0:33:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,提咆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}T'Pau.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.82,0:33:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你开口了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thee speaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.86,0:33:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.20,0:33:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,…并不了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...does not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.95,0:33:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,决定已经做出了，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The choice has been made, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.49,0:33:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,由他来决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is up to him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.29,0:33:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他不了解情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He does not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.46,0:33:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我会参加决斗，提咆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will do what I must, T'Pau.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.38,0:33:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝不是和他决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.88,0:34:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他的血液不会燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His blood does not burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.51,0:34:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.97,0:34:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,人们说瓦肯人的血是稀薄的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is said thy Vulcan blood is thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.56,0:34:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你是瓦肯人还是人类？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are thee Vulcan or are thee human?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.36,0:34:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我会燃烧，提咆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I burn, T'Pau.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.24,0:34:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛就是火焰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My eyes are flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.12,0:34:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心脏就是火焰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My heart is flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.75,0:34:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你有权决定，提咆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thee has the power, T'Pau.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.88,0:34:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,以父之名，请禁止吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the name of my fathers, forbid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.22,0:34:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,提咆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}T'Pau.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.02,0:34:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我请求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I plead with thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.94,0:34:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我乞求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I beg.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.16,0:34:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经用瓦肯传统证明了你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thee has prided thyself on thy Vulcan heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.49,0:34:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,已经决定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.14,0:35:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我拒绝，史波克会怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happens to Spock if I decline?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.42,0:35:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个代表会被选出与他决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Another champion will be selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.40,0:35:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要干涉，寇克，不要乱动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do not interfere, Kirk. Keep thy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.37,0:35:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能决斗，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't do it, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.67,0:35:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不能？ - 不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I can't? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.38,0:35:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她说你不受制于他们的律法和习俗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She said that their laws and customs were not binding on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.71,0:35:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但你说史波克可能打不过他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you said Spock might not be able to handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.84,0:35:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能打晕史波克而不伤害他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, if I can knock Spock out without really hurting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.85,0:35:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在这样的天气？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In this climate?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.60,0:35:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不热死你也会呼吸不过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the heat doesn't get you, the thin air will.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.46,0:36:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你做不到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.17,0:36:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果出了麻烦我就退出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I get into any trouble, I'll quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.92,0:36:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那史波克赢，大不了丢面子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Spock wins, and honour is satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.38,0:36:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 吉姆，听我说，如果… - 老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Jim, listen, if you... - Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.72,0:36:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的大副也是我朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's my first officer and my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.34,0:36:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我违背了舰队的命令把他带到这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I disregarded Starfleet orders to bring him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.72,0:36:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还有，这是提咆，是瓦肯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Another thing, that's T'Pau, a Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.90,0:36:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所有瓦肯人都在这了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All of Vulcan in one package.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.57,0:36:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么能在她面前退缩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How can I back out in front of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.17,0:36:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么决定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.02,0:36:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克，决定吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk, decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.82,0:37:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I accept the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.87,0:37:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为争夺提普灵的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here begins the act of combat
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.83,0:37:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,决斗开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for possession of the woman T'Pring.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.75,0:37:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就好象时间之初，现也如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As it was at the time of the beginning, so it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.88,0:37:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,把里尔耙带上来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bring forth the lirpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.60,0:37:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们在这关活下来…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If both survive the lirpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.40,0:37:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,…那决斗就改用安乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...combat will continue with the ahn'woon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.57,0:37:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果都活下来”，什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you mean, "if both survive"?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.28,0:37:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,决斗以死结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This combat is to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.04,0:38:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, wait a minute, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.71,0:38:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谁说决斗以死结束了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who said anything about a fight to the death?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.96,0:38:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是朋友，强迫他们互相残杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These men are friends. To force them to fight till one of them is killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.42,0:38:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不允许你们再演这出了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can forgive such a display only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.14,0:38:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,决斗已经提出，并已依法接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Challenge was given and lawfully accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.65,0:38:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,决斗已经开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.03,0:38:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不准任何人干预\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let no one interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.95,0:40:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，不要！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.51,0:40:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是瓦肯的骑士精神吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this Vulcan chivalry?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.34,0:40:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,空气对寇克来说太热太稀薄了，他适应不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The air is too hot and thin for Kirk. He's not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.14,0:40:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,空气如此有什么办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The air is the air. What can be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.02,0:40:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以用这个弥补空气不足和高温\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can compensate for the atmosphere and the temperature with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.52,0:40:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,至少给寇克一个战斗的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least it will give Kirk a fighting chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.32,0:40:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,准\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thee may proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.83,0:40:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须杀了他，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're going to have to kill him, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.55,0:40:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kill Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.59,0:40:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我们来瓦肯的目的，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not what we came to Vulcan for, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.39,0:40:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.93,0:41:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是三氧复合剂，能帮助你呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a tri-ox compound. It'll help you breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.06,0:41:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 小心点 - 谨遵医嘱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Now be careful. - Sound medical advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.24,0:41:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,上安乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ahn'woon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.59,0:42:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,放手，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get your hands off of him, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.55,0:42:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.77,0:42:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.57,0:43:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,请节哀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I grieve with thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.62,0:43:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 麦考伊请求联系进取号 - 进取号乌乎拉在此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- McCoy to Enterprise. - Enterprise. Lieutenant Uhura here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.92,0:43:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请传送室准备传送登陆小队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have the Transporter Room stand by to beam up the landing party.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.81,0:43:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很讽刺，但是史波克先生，由你下命令了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As strange as it may seem, Mr. Spock, you're in command now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.69,0:43:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么指令吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.36,0:43:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.53,0:43:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我一会儿就跟上你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll follow you up in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.70,0:43:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你让契诃夫先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will instruct Mr. Chekov
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.21,0:43:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,设计一条去最近星际基地的线路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to plot a course for the nearest star base...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.30,0:44:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,…我要在那里向当局自首\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...where I must surrender myself to the authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.44,0:44:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,提普灵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}T'Pring.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.30,0:44:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 解释一下 - 解释什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Explain. - Specify.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.74,0:44:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.45,0:44:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你选择我的舰长做代表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And why you chose my captain as your champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.10,0:44:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我和斯通两情相悦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stonn wanted me, I wanted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.17,0:44:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白，你为什么会喜欢他而不喜欢我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see no logic in preferring Stonn over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.63,0:44:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个名人，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have become much known among our people, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.97,0:44:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至说是传奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.31,0:44:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,时间流转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And as the years went by,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.89,0:44:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我意识到我不想成为一个传奇的配偶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I came to know that I did not want to be the consort of a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.23,0:44:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是根据律法，我只能通过卡里菲和你离婚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But by the laws of our people, I could only divorce you by the kal-if-fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.78,0:44:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,当然还有斯通的原因，他很爱慕我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was also Stonn, who wanted very much to be my consort,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.36,0:45:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱慕他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I wanted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.16,0:45:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的舰长赢了，他不会要我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If your captain were victor, he would not want me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.70,0:45:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就可以拥有斯通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and so I would have Stonn.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.79,0:45:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你赢了，你会放我走，因为我选择了决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you were victor, you would free me because I had dared to challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.08,0:45:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那我还能和斯通在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and again I would have Stonn.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.67,0:45:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,即使你没放了我，那也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if you did not free me, it would be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.34,0:45:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你会离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For you would be gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.18,0:45:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我拥有你的名分和财产\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I would have your name and your property,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.60,0:45:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而斯通仍在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Stonn would still be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.60,0:45:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,非常有逻辑性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.60,0:45:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,完美无瑕的逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Flawlessly logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.69,0:45:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 斯通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I am honoured. - Stonn.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.36,0:45:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她是你的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.87,0:45:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,过一段时间，你会发现拥有…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After a time, you may find that having...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.50,0:45:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,并不像爱慕一样让人开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...is not so pleasing a thing after all as wanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.21,0:45:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这解释不通…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is not logical...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.01,0:45:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,…但确是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...but it is often true.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.05,0:46:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是史波克，请传送我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock here. Stand by to beam up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.61,0:46:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,生生不息，繁荣昌盛，提咆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Live long, T'Pau, and prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.74,0:46:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,生生不息，繁荣昌盛，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Live long and prosper, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.00,0:46:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕我都做不到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I shall do neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.41,0:46:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了我的舰长和我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have killed my captain and my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.81,0:46:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.71,0:47:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，我想辞职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, I shall be resigning my commission immediately, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.50,0:47:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我会感激你能做最后的安排\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I would appreciate your making the final arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.63,0:47:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克，我… - 医生，请听我说完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock, I... - Doctor, please, let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.47,0:47:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的罪行没有借口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There can be no excuse for the crime of which I am guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.30,0:47:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想狡辩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I intend to offer no defence.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.02,0:47:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,另外，我会请史考特立刻接手舰船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Furthermore, I will order Mr. Scott to take immediate command of this vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.69,0:47:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 难道你不应该先和我打个招呼吗？ - 舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Shouldn't you check with me first? - Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.15,0:47:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.16,0:47:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你很高兴，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm pleased to see you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.33,0:47:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You seem uninjured.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.04,0:47:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点搞不清了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am at something of a loss to understand it, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.75,0:47:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怪麦考伊吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blame McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.21,0:47:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他给我注射的不是三氧复合剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was no tri-ox compound he shot me with.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.90,0:47:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种模拟死亡的麻醉剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He slipped in a neural paralyzer. Knocked me out. Simulated death.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.60,0:47:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 确实如此 - 护士，你介意给我们点空间吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Indeed. - Nurse, would you mind, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.36,0:48:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，婚礼和那个女孩后来怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, what happened down there? The girl, the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.19,0:48:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，对了，那个女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, yes, the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.78,0:48:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思的是我在决斗的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Most interesting. It must have been the combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.99,0:48:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当我杀了舰长后，对提普灵完全失去了兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I thought I had killed the Captain, I found I'd lost all interest in T'Pring.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.20,0:48:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那种疯狂也消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The madness was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.04,0:48:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克在此 - 寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk here. - Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.71,0:48:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,来自舰队指挥部的消息，最高优先级\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Message from Starfleet Command. Top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.38,0:48:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,转播过来，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Relay it, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.47,0:48:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,应提咆的要求，进取号绕道去瓦肯的行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Response to T'Pau's request for diversion of Enterprise to Vulcan
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.42,0:48:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,予以批准，迟到不予追究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}hereby approved. Any reasonable delay granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.15,0:48:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,寇马克上将，舰队指挥部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Komack, Admiral, Starfleet Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.40,0:48:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,迟到一点，但能被赦免太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A little late, but I'm glad they're seeing it our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.78,0:48:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还是提咆的影响大，他们不能拒绝她的请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How about that T'Pau? They couldn't turn her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.40,0:48:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,契诃夫先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.20,0:48:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,设计好线路去牛郎星6号，准备好即刻出发，寇克退出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}lay in a course for Altair VI. Leave orbit when ready. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.12,0:48:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's just one thing, Mr. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.75,0:48:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉我你看到吉姆还活着的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you can't tell me when you saw Jim alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.75,0:48:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有激动得想要跳起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you weren't on the verge of giving an emotional scene
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.09,0:48:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,激动得要把马都拉倒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that would've brought the house down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.92,0:49:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只是理智上的解脱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Merely my quite logical relief
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.26,0:49:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还好舰队没有失去这样一位高水平的舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that Starfleet had not lost a highly proficient captain.
